So, I just got back from Anime Boston a little while ago.&nbsp; I did not get a badge there because, due to the hours spent waiting in line, I had about one hour before I had to go home, and I really don't think that is worth $30.&nbsp; So, I spent all morning/afternoon there, and now I have to go to work for another 5 hours.
&gt;_&lt;
I hate my life sometimes.&nbsp; I really do.

Okay, guys.

You are now officially reading the very last public entry on my journal.&nbsp; All others, from this point on, will be friends-locked.&nbsp; 

If you've been lurking in the background until now and don't want to be left out of the fun, comment on this entry and I'll add you.
